# Graphify visualization — generated output is regeneratable via regen.py
# and kept local-only; the hand-edited source files are versioned. Use
# `graphify-out/*` (not `graphify-out/`) so the un-ignore patterns can
# re-include individual source files (a directory exclusion would block
# any negation underneath).
graphify-out/*
!graphify-out/regen.py
!graphify-out/orchestration.json
!graphify-out/style.css
!graphify-out/REGEN.md

# Per-machine Claude Code + direnv state
.claude/
.envrc
